high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Take the alarmclock from the sink.
Turn around and go to the desk in the bedroom.
Put the alarmclock on the desk.
Turn left and go near the bed.
Take another alarmclock from the bed.
Turn around and go near the desk.
Put the alarmclock on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Collect the AlarmClock and placed it on the Desk.

high_descs: Turn left to head down the passage and reach the sink in the bathroom.
Pick up the alarm clock from the sink.
Turn around to exit the bathroom and head right to reach the desk on the right.
Put the alarmclock on the desk.
Turn left to reach the bed.
Pick up the alarmclock from the bed.
Turn right to reach the desk next to the bed.
Put the alarm clock on the desk with the other clock.
anns.task_desc: Put two AlarmClocks on the Desk.

high_descs: Turn around and take right,head toward the sink.
Take the alarmclock from the sink.
Turn around, move then take left and move forward, turn right go straight to the desk.
Put the alarmclock on the desk.
Turn around then take right and go to the bed, turn right.
Pick up the alarmclock from the bed.
Turn right and move forward to desk.
Put the alarmclock on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Get the AlarmClock and place it on the Desk.
